videos.headline: Auburn fumbles on fourth down
videos.description: Auburn runs the ball on 4th-and-1, with JaTarvious Whitlow coughing up the ball and Tulane recovering.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn fumbles on fourth down) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hastings spins past defender for Auburn TD
videos.description: Bo Nix finds Will Hastings open downfield and Hastings spins past a defender en route to the end zone for a 31-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hastings spins past defender for Auburn TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stove finds the crease for 4-yard score
videos.description: Eli Stove gets the handoff and runs through the hole for a 4-yard Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stove finds the crease for 4-yard score) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulane's Mooney climbs the ladder for first down
videos.description: On 3rd-and-11, Tulane's Justin McMillan throws high over the middle of the field to a leaping Darnell Mooney for a 22-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulane's Mooney climbs the ladder for first down) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Dinson hustles for the INT
videos.description: Tulane's Justin McMillan tries to throw the ball away but Auburn's Jeremiah Dinson speeds over and dives for the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn's Dinson hustles for the INT) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Whitlow scores from the Wildcat
videos.description: JaTarvious Whitlow takes the snap from the Wildcat formation and follows good blocking on the far side of the field for a 14-yard Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Whitlow scores from the Wildcat) 2019/09/07 ESHEET
